         <abstract id="aspace_b860c9b5e7de23b29b2cea8500d30681">The collection comprises manuscript material concerning Matthew Shepperson, who was a portrait copyist, art instructor to English lords and ladies, and a collector of portraits.  It contains correspondence, financial records, and additional documents.</abstract>
